sequenceDiagram
    actor Doctor
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant SQL as SQL Agent
    participant Vec as Vector Agent
    participant Sum as Summarizer
    
    Doctor->>UI: "Give me details about..."
    UI->>Orch: POST /query
    
    par Parallel Execution
        Orch->>SQL: POST /query
        Orch->>Vec: POST /query
    and
        SQL->>SQL: Generate & Run SQL
        Vec->>Vec: Embed & Retrieve
    end
    
    SQL-->>Orch: Structured Data / "No Data"
    Vec-->>Orch: Unstructured Context
    
    Orch->>Sum: POST /summarize (Query + SQL + Vector)
    Sum-->>Orch: Final Synthesized Answer
    
    Orch-->>UI: JSON Response + Timings
    UI->>Doctor: Display Answer + Trace
